#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.173"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.173:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.173:0.2"
msgid "18. Sañcetaniyavagga"
msgstr "18. Intention"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: mahākoṭṭhitasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.173:0.3"
msgid "173. Mahākoṭṭhikasutta"
msgstr "173. With Mahākoṭṭhita"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.161"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: mahākoṭṭhiko → mahākoṭṭhito (bj)
msgctxt "an4.173:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā sāriputtena saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita went up to Venerable Sāriputta, and exchanged "
"greetings with him."

msgctxt "an4.173:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho āyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, Mahākoṭṭhita sat down "
"to one side, and said to Sāriputta:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:2.1"
msgid "“Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthaññaṃ kiñcī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, when the six fields of contact have faded away and ceased with "
"nothing left over, does something else exist?”"

# As per BB, comm gllesses with me havem bhani; elsewhere ma hevam and ma hevam avaca are variant readings.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:3.1"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, āvuso”."
msgstr "“Don’t put it like that, reverend.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:4.1"
msgid ""
"“Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā natthaññaṃ kiñcī”ti?"
msgstr "“Does nothing else exist?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:5.1"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, āvuso”."
msgstr "“Don’t put it like that, reverend.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:6.1"
msgid ""
"“Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthi ca natthi ca aññaṃ "
"kiñcī”ti?"
msgstr "“Do both something else and nothing else exist?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:7.1"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, āvuso”."
msgstr "“Don’t put it like that, reverend.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:8.1"
msgid ""
"“Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā nevatthi no natthaññaṃ "
"kiñcī”ti?"
msgstr "“Do neither something else nor nothing else exist?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:9.1"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, āvuso”."
msgstr "“Don’t put it like that, reverend.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:10.1"
msgid ""
"“‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti "
"puṭṭho samāno ‘mā hevaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, when asked whether—when the six fields of contact have faded away "
"and ceased with nothing left over—something else exists, you say ‘don’t put "
"it like that’."

msgctxt "an4.173:10.2"
msgid ""
"‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā natthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti "
"puṭṭho samāno:"
msgstr "When asked whether nothing else exists, "

msgctxt "an4.173:10.3"
msgid "‘mā hevaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi."
msgstr "you say ‘don’t put it like that’."

msgctxt "an4.173:10.4"
msgid ""
"‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthi ca natthi ca aññaṃ "
"kiñcī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno:"
msgstr "When asked whether both something else and nothing else exist,"

msgctxt "an4.173:10.5"
msgid "‘mā hevaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi."
msgstr "you say ‘don’t put it like that’."

msgctxt "an4.173:10.6"
msgid ""
"‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā nevatthi no natthaññaṃ "
"kiñcī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno:"
msgstr "When asked whether neither something else nor nothing else exist, "

msgctxt "an4.173:10.7"
msgid "‘mā hevaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi."
msgstr "you say ‘don’t put it like that’."

msgctxt "an4.173:10.8"
msgid "Yathā kathaṃ pana, āvuso, imassa bhāsitassa attho daṭṭhabbo”ti?"
msgstr "How then should we see the meaning of this statement?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.162"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an4.173:11.1"
msgid ""
"“‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti "
"vadaṃ appapañcaṃ papañceti."
msgstr ""
"“If you say that, ‘When the six fields of contact have faded away and ceased "
"with nothing left over, something else exists’, you’re proliferating the "
"unproliferated."

msgctxt "an4.173:11.2"
msgid ""
"‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā natthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti "
"vadaṃ appapañcaṃ papañceti."
msgstr ""
"If you say that ‘nothing else exists’, you’re proliferating the "
"unproliferated."

msgctxt "an4.173:11.3"
msgid ""
"‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthi ca natthi ca aññaṃ "
"kiñcī’ti, iti vadaṃ appapañcaṃ papañceti."
msgstr ""
"If you say that ‘both something else and nothing else exist’, you’re "
"proliferating the unproliferated."

msgctxt "an4.173:11.4"
msgid ""
"‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā nevatthi no natthaññaṃ "
"kiñcī’ti, iti vadaṃ appapañcaṃ papañceti."
msgstr ""
"If you say that ‘neither something else nor nothing else exists’, you’re "
"proliferating the unproliferated."

msgctxt "an4.173:11.5"
msgid "Yāvatā, āvuso, channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ gati tāvatā papañcassa gati;"
msgstr ""
"The scope of the six fields of contact extends as far as the scope of "
"proliferation."

msgctxt "an4.173:11.6"
msgid "yāvatā papañcassa gati tāvatā channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ gati."
msgstr ""
"The scope of proliferation extends as far as the scope of the six fields of "
"contact."

msgctxt "an4.173:11.7"
msgid ""
"Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā papañcanirodho "
"papañcavūpasamo”ti."
msgstr ""
"When the six fields of contact fade away and cease with nothing left over, "
"proliferation stops and is stilled.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.173:11.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
